thread.title: Ash Shah
thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da Ash Shah

author: Ash Shah
title: Ash Shah
text: Bought my Maui Jims which were on offer. They were very competitively priced from what was on sale in Australia (stores and online). Love these sunnies. Delivery was superfast considering they came from Italy but as FedEx was used as the carrier they kept you in the loop as to where they were at any point in time. As I was not at home on the delivery date they delivered to my work the next day so very pleased. Excellent service, fast delivery and 100% genuine article. Will recommend and use again.
